ころで、Direct2Dスクロール版、誰か試した方いますか？ 自分のところでは問題なく動いているようですが。","ts":"1514293929.000042","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"あ、ごめんなさい。やるつもりでできてなかった。","ts":"1514295156.000084","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"Hwndレンダーターゲット、EndDrawで16msの待ちが発生してた。\nあれっ、DCレンダーターゲットやGDIだと表示が間引かれてたってこと？","ts":"1514259571.000060","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"あれかな","ts":"1514261199.000051","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"16msだと 60FPS とかで、垂直同期待ちとかしてないかな?","ts":"1514261213.000001","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"}]
